title: Malta Money Supply M0
description: Money Supply M0 in Malta increased to 1491.40 EUR Million in September from 1484.99 EUR Million in August of 2022. Money Supply M0 in Malta averaged 955.56 EUR Million from 2001 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1526.83 EUR Million in June of 2022 and a record low of 599.35 EUR Million in February of 2009. Malta Money Supply M0 is the most liquid measure of the money supply including coins and notes in circulation and other assets that are easily convertible into cash. Money Supply M0 and M1, are also known as narrow money. This page provides - Malta Money Supply M0 - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Malta
